<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>a. Good season!</p>
<p>b. Theodotos loves Hypsikles</p>
<p>c. God, help!</p>
<p>d. <gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> triumphs <gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></p>
</div>
